  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a wok or large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add oxtail and onions to the pan, cook until lightly browned on all sides.",
    "Mix in tomato puree, chili powder, cumin seeds, sugar, salt, and lime juice. Stir well until the mixture comes together into a sauce.",
    "Simmer for 15-20 minutes or until the oxtail is tender but not falling apart.",
    "Stir in cilantro leaves just before serving."
